text: Ena is a genus of air-breathing land snails, terrestrial pulmonate gastropod mollusks in the family Enidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Ena include: * Ena montana * Ena nogellii (Roth, 1850) - synonym: Buliminus ponticus Retowski, 1886Hausdorf B.
